Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.06,Main,,0,0,0,,A
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.35,0:00:05.69,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Maybe I should shoot the shit out of\N this fatty and see what happens! {Line 2-8 are copy pasted from my QC -Gyro}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.31,0:00:07.32,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.32,0:00:09.23,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,Th-That was close...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.23,0:00:12.32,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,He would have got me if I \N hadn't returned to normal size!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.78,0:00:18.16,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,If your Stand wasn't \N basically harmless by now...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.16,0:00:19.58,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,...I would have been killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.58,0:00:22.04,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,I-I didn't get him! {end copy pasta}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.75,0:00:25.92,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,D-Dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.25,0:00:32.47,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Is Aerosmith's power shrinking \N as I get smaller and smaller? {Line rework by Jules suggestion -Gyro}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.01,0:00:34.68,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,He's on the move again!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.68,0:00:36.51,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Come back, Aerosmith!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.76,0:00:43.23,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Th-This is really pissing me off, \N but I gotta find a hiding place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.23,0:00:45.40,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,The motherfucker's getting desperate, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.40,0:00:50.57,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,If he finds me, he'll do anything \N to get me to cough up where the boss's daughter is.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.41,0:00:56.86,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,I-It's so far away!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.53,0:00:59.58,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,This sidewalk is way too big!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.04,0:01:05.75,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Move it! \N You're in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.72,0:01:15.76,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Sh-Shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.06,0:01:27.81,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,Got you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.81,0:01:29.98,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,Guess you're screwed. {"shou ga nee na..."}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.27,0:01:32.65,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,Really put me through the wringer, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.11,0:01:38.11,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,Ain't no one running from me \N if I get them with Little Feat. {Anyone affected by Little Feat's ability \N can never escape.}{Eh... on this phrasing. It feels overly literal. -Starfish}{Trying this. Don't particularly care for keeping 能力, since this should be implicit enough. -JMFW/Toa}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.11,0:01:39.70,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,Now talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.70,0:01:44.41,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,Where are Buccellati and your friends \N hiding the boss's daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.41,0:01:46.66,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,K-Kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.00,0:01:49.63,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Dammit, just kill me already!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.63,0:01:56.97,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,You really think I'm desperate enough \N to give up where my friends are hiding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.05,0:02:05.60,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,750)}Narancia Ghirga was born in 1984 \N under the sign of Leo.{Is the fade too much? Remove it if so but I think it's fine. -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.68,0:02:08.56,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,When he was ten years old...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:11.23,Flashback,Mela,0,0,0,,N-Narancia...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.57,0:02:16.61,Flashback,Narancia,0,0,0,,I'm right here, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.03,0:02:21.12,Flashback,Narancia,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.75,0:02:27.25,Flashback,Narancia,0,0,0,,Hey, Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.87,0:02:30.21,Flashback,Narancia,0,0,0,,About Mom's eye disease...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.01,0:02:39.51,Flashback,Narancia,0,0,0,,I hate you... {"kusoyarou" translated as "I hate you"? For NARANCIA? idk about that, man... -Starfish}{I think the idea here is that he's still relatively innocent at this point... but if it's really bugging you, maybe bump it up a little. -JMFW}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.01,0:02:45.01,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Thus Narancia started down the path \N that would bring him to the present day.
