Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.52,0:04:20.28,Flashback,Narancia,0,0,0,,{\an8}Can you help me with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.11,0:04:24.28,Flashback,Narancia,0,0,0,,How many minutes do you think \N it'll take to walk here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.61,0:04:29.04,Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,{\an8}Minutes? That'll take hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.28,0:04:26.74,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Narancia rebelled against his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.74,0:04:33.62,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,He got through each day by stealing food \N and sleeping over at the houses of his delinquent friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.62,0:04:35.08,Flashback,Narancia,0,0,0,,It went great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.08,0:04:37.84,Flashback,Narancia,0,0,0,,It's all because you told us \N about that shop, Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.84,0:04:40.38,Flashback,Bro,0,0,0,,You sure you don't need to be at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.38,0:04:42.55,Flashback,Bro,0,0,0,,You got an actual \N decent home to go back to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:44.76,Flashback,Narancia,0,0,0,,Like I give a shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.13,0:04:48.47,Flashback,Narancia,0,0,0,,The most important thing \N in the world is friendship! {when did this become fairy tail -J}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:50.43,Flashback,Bro,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.85,0:04:53.06,Flashback,Bro,0,0,0,,You should dye your hair blond like mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.06,0:04:55.52,Flashback,Bro,0,0,0,,Chicks won't be able \N to keep their hands off you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:04:57.27,Flashback,Narancia,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:05:00.69,Flashback,Human being,0,0,0,,What? Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.69,0:05:02.69,Flashback,Narancia,0,0,0,,Pretty cool, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:04.53,Flashback,Human being,0,0,0,,You look stupid as hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.53,0:05:06.24,Flashback,Narancia,0,0,0,,Hey, where's Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.24,0:05:08.62,Flashback,Human being,0,0,0,,Who knows? \N Haven't seen him in days.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.91,0:05:10.12,Flashback,Narancia,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.12,0:05:12.12,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,But the next day...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.96,0:05:16.29,Flashback,Narancia,0,0,0,,You assholes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.41,0:05:16.54,Flashback,Cop,0,0,0,,{\an8}Spread 'em! Up against the wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.54,0:05:20.17,Flashback,Cop,0,0,0,,{\an8}You little punk! \NYou're going to juvie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:20.17,Flashback,Narancia,0,0,0,,What the hell are you talking about?! \N I wouldn't steal!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.17,0:05:20.96,Flashback,Narancia,0,0,0,,I'm not a{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.42,0:05:24.17,Flashback,Cop,0,0,0,,Don't lie! \N We got a witness!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.17,0:05:25.01,Flashback,Narancia,0,0,0,,Wha{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.84,0:05:28.55,Flashback,Lady,0,0,0,,That's him! \N This blond brat is the culprit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.55,0:05:29.68,Flashback,Narancia,0,0,0,,N-No I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:33.27,Flashback,Lady,0,0,0,,I'm sure of it! \N He beat me and took off with my money!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:35.23,Flashback,Narancia,0,0,0,,Quit lying, you crusty old bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.23,0:05:36.73,Flashback,Narancia,0,0,0,,I didn't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.81,0:05:41.32,Flashback,Cop,0,0,0,,Just admit you're guilty, \N you fucking punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.32,0:05:43.03,Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,Hey! \N You're going too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.03,0:05:44.82,Flashback,Cop,0,0,0,,You saw it too, right, lawyer?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.82,0:05:47.66,Flashback,Cop,0,0,0,,He was trying to have another go at her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:55.00,Flashback,Narancia,0,0,0,,A robbery...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.12,0:05:58.83,Flashback,Narancia,0,0,0,,A blond brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:01.09,Flashback,Narancia,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.80,0:06:06.88,Flashback,Narancia,0,0,0,,No, that's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.88,0:06:09.26,Flashback,Narancia,0,0,0,,Quit thinking up shit like that, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:16.48,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,A year later, when Narancia was released from juvenile hall, \N his eye was in bad shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:22.69,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,The wound from the officer's punch \N had become infected and seemingly wouldn't heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.94,0:06:29.70,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,When he returned to town, \N strange rumors began circulating among his friends. {Don't fucking even -J}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:31.03,Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,Look at him...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.03,0:06:34.29,Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,I heard his mom died \N from an eye disease, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.12,0:06:36.62,Flashback,Narancia,0,0,0,,How do they know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.62,0:06:38.87,Flashback,Narancia,0,0,0,,I only ever told Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.87,0:06:41.71,Flashback,Bro,0,0,0,,Wow, they already let you out?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.96,0:06:45.30,Flashback,Bro,0,0,0,,Don't infect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.30,0:06:47.51,Flashback,Bro,0,0,0,,You better stay the fuck back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.97,0:06:54.85,Flashback,Narancia,0,0,0,,It can't be... But Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.85,0:06:57.68,Flashback,Narancia,0,0,0,,He felt trapped, \N so he used me as a scapegoat...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.14,0:07:02.90,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,The one most afraid of these rumors \N concerning his disease...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:05.15,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,...was Narancia himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.57,0:07:07.65,Flashback,Narancia,0,0,0,,This is fate...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:10.36,Flashback,Narancia,0,0,0,,Soon... just like Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:12.57,Flashback,Narancia,0,0,0,,...I'm gonna die from this disease!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.99,0:07:16.08,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,He truly believed it. \NHe had nowhere left to turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:18.16,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,He was all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.66,0:07:22.04,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Narancia had given up on life \N at the young age of fifteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.04,0:07:24.75,Flashback,Zoomer,0,0,0,,How terrible... He's just a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.75,0:07:27.51,Flashback,Boomer,0,0,0,,I feel sorry for him, \N but we shouldn't get involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.60,0:07:46.48,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,The young man brought Narancia into a restaurant, \N then told the waiter and his friend waiting at the table... {I think this is a bit more appropriate. Fugo looks like a teenager here, not a little kid -G}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.48,0:07:48.78,Flashback,Fugo,0,0,0,,I'd like to buy him a plate of spaghetti!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.78,0:07:50.19,Flashback,Fugo,0,0,0,,Would that be acceptable?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.36,0:07:55.78,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,His friend at the table \N didn't ask any questions...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.08,0:07:58.49,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,...nor did he give him a look of disgust.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.49,0:08:04.25,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,He simply set the plate of spaghetti he had ordered for himself \N right in front of the filthy child.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.67,0:08:09.38,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,He then helped the child \N receive the treatment he required.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.76,0:08:11.13,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Three weeks later...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.67,0:08:15.14,Flashback,Narancia,0,0,0,,Why'd you do all this for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.14,0:08:16.10,Flashback,Bruno,0,0,0,,No reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.47,0:08:19.93,Flashback,Bruno,0,0,0,,If you like, you can stay at my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.93,0:08:22.85,Flashback,Bruno,0,0,0,,But children like you \N should still live with their parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.85,0:08:25.31,Flashback,Bruno,0,0,0,,Also, go back to school. Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.31,0:08:29.15,Flashback,Narancia,0,0,0,,U-Umm, are you a gangster?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:35.16,Flashback,Narancia,0,0,0,,I don't wanna go home...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:37.12,Flashback,Narancia,0,0,0,,Please let me work for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.12,0:08:40.29,Flashback,Bruno,0,0,0,,Don't be so naïve, you little punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.91,0:08:44.75,Flashback,Bruno,0,0,0,,Say more stupid shit like that \N and I'll punch you in the face!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.21,0:08:51.67,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,As instructed, Narancia returned home \N and began going back to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.21,0:08:56.39,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,However, he never trusted his father again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.10,0:09:05.77,Flashback,Narancia,0,0,0,,Why was he so tough on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.60,0:09:09.23,Flashback,Narancia,0,0,0,,I'm nothing special.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.23,0:09:10.27,Flashback,Narancia,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.98,0:09:17.70,Flashback,Narancia,0,0,0,,It's not like he was mad because he hated me, \N and I don't think he was trying to insult me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.70,0:09:21.20,Flashback,Narancia,0,0,0,,It felt nothing like when my dad \N or the cops get mad at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:26.21,Flashback,Narancia,0,0,0,,The way he treated me \N makes me feel encouraged!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.67,0:09:28.17,Flashback,Narancia,0,0,0,,Real men...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.09,0:09:31.67,Flashback,Narancia,0,0,0,,...should work for guys like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.67,0:09:38.59,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Six months later, Narancia went to see one of the capos \N of the organization, Polpo, without telling Buccellati...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.10,0:09:41.68,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,...and passed his test.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.60,0:09:48.60,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,Narancia, if you're gonna cough up \N where his daughter is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.60,0:09:51.82,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,...now would be the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.82,0:09:55.40,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,The girl you're trying to kidnap \N isn't a gangster or a criminal!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.40,0:09:56.90,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,She's just a normal girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.90,0:10:01.12,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Buccellati fucking hates anyone who'd kidnap an innocent, \N and it's got nothing to do with orders! {Fix, also nice typo}{Fix, also nice typo}{Fix, also nice typo}{Fix, also nice typo}{Fix, also nice typo}{Added more comments -J}{left the first five comments, same as the rest. added a naughty word and slightly shortened the line to get it under 20 CPS. Justification: listened to the JP. Doesn't really say anything about following orders, just says that the Bucc doesn't kidnap innocent people for the hell of it. He also stresses the hate. -JMFW/Toa}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.41,0:10:03.16,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Good people don't do that shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:05.70,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,We swore we'd protect her...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:08.37,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,...and we'll keep that promise no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.46,0:10:14.63,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,Could you stop it with the bullshit?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.63,0:10:16.34,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,Guess you just don't get it... {"shou ga nee na..."}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.84,0:10:20.22,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,All this shit about your friends \N and protecting this bitch...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:23.31,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,That's not what we're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:30.52,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,What I'm telling you is that if we can off the boss, his drug operation worth hundreds of billions is ours for the taking.{Checked. "sen-oku" is indeed one hundred billion, meaning "nanzen-oku" does indeed mean "hundreds of billions". I feel I must be careful with stuff like this because, y'know... episode 1. -Starfish}{"defeat" -> "off" because we keep using "defeat" for 倒す when it's clearly intended to mean they're gonna dispose of him (probably in a trash bag or something idk i'm not a mobster) -JMFW/Toa}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.90,0:10:32.23,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Y-You motherfucker!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.69,0:10:37.44,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,Hundreds of billions!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.44,0:10:40.95,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,That much money's \N gotta be worth a few lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.95,0:10:42.95,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,That shit's ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.95,0:10:44.83,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,No backing out now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:50.04,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,If that girl has the boss's blood flowing through her veins, \N she's gotta have a Stand ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.58,0:10:53.50,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,The boss doesn't want \N anyone finding out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:57.34,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,We'll definitely figure out who the boss is \N through his daughter's ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.34,0:11:02.47,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,The boss's daughter is the only hint \N we got to figure out who he really is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.80,0:11:05.93,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,What? She's a Stand user?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.93,0:11:07.18,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,Hey, did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.18,0:11:10.98,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,There's a spider in South America \N called the southern black widow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.98,0:11:14.44,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,Apparently, its venom can even kill humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.73,0:11:17.07,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,The spider I have here isn't harmful to humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.07,0:11:21.28,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,I actually caught it in the sewers earlier. \N It's completely harmless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:23.91,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.91,0:11:28.16,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,Even normal spiders bite, \N and this one is still venomous! {If you think that this blatantly contradicts his previous claim that it isn't a venomous spider... you would be completely right. I guess the intent here is that it's not venomous TO NORMAL FULL-SIZED HUMANS, but... he does in fact phrase it first as "It's not a venomous spider" and then later "It does have venom". -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.16,0:11:33.46,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,Venomous enough to paralyze \N and eat puny little insects!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.16,0:11:29.87,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,{\an8}Y-You aren't gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.46,0:11:34.50,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Aerosmith!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.05,0:11:37.13,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,Watch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.51,0:11:42.84,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,I already told you, \N your Stand is fucking worthless!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:49.31,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,This bottle is gonna be your arena, Narancia!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.94,0:11:53.90,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Y-You motherfucker! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.86,0:12:00.74,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,It's looking at you! \NCheck it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.11,0:12:04.74,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,It's watching you with all eight of its eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.74,0:12:06.83,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Open up! \NOpen the bottle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.24,0:12:09.45,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.45,0:12:14.54,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,Listen up! \N Even if it bites you, you won't die right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.54,0:12:19.38,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,First it'll stop you from moving \N by paralyzing your muscles.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.71,0:12:23.18,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,But once you're trapped and can't move, \N you'll be in for some real shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.63,0:12:28.60,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,It'll start injecting you with \N even more venom and digestive juices!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:37.61,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,Your insides will be melted like a vanilla milkshake, \N and then it'll suck you right up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.61,0:12:40.23,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,And best of all, \N you'll be conscious the whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.23,0:12:43.57,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,If you ever feel like talking, \N you can do that while it's eating you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.57,0:12:47.53,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,But I'd recommend talking \N while you still have the chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.53,0:12:49.83,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,...and tell me where the boss's daughter is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.54,0:12:55.79,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,I really don't wanna see someone \N get turned to mush and eaten by a spider!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.38,0:12:59.17,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,I-It's so fast! {Spider sakuga. -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.42,0:13:01.63,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,You asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.67,0:13:05.05,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,A glass shard?! {Seems like the audio skips here. Mixing error on david pro's part?}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.80,0:13:07.51,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,He's had that with him this whole time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.72,0:13:09.97,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,W-Webbing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.43,0:13:11.89,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,When did it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.65,0:13:21.11,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,It bit him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.74,0:13:29.53,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,You can't move now that \Nyour muscles are freaking out, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:31.29,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,Just hurry up and tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.29,0:13:33.91,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,This is your last chance\N if you don't wanna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.83,0:13:38.29,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Fuck... Like hell I'll tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.29,0:13:40.92,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,{\an8}Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.29,0:13:42.25,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,Looks like it's injecting its \N digestive juices into you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.25,0:13:44.01,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,You're gonna melt...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.47,0:13:46.30,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.63,0:13:55.02,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,Lookie here... This must've fallen out of your pocket \N when you took out that glass shard...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.27,0:14:00.44,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,Y'know... maybe I don't need you after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.86,0:14:02.61,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,It's a map of the city...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.61,0:14:05.11,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,A road map, at that. \NAnd best of all...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.44,0:14:07.82,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,It's been marked up with a pencil!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.82,0:14:09.82,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,Just so you wouldn't get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.20,0:14:12.33,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,Are you fucking stupid? {i am wood}{duuuuh stoopid}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:16.04,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,I can find out where you came from \N if I follow the directions in reverse!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.46,0:14:18.37,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,A vineyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:22.29,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,You came from a vineyard about\N twenty kilometers southeast!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.29,0:14:24.76,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,Grazie, Narancia!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.76,0:14:29.22,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,Now that thing can just eat you and \N lay its eggs inside you or whatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.22,0:14:31.30,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,...dipshit!{This is perhaps not hyper necessary and could be chalked up to character writing, but note that he uses the same word here as on line 208: "manuke." -Starfish}
Comment: 0,0:14:32.93,0:14:32.97,Main,,0,0,0,,C
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.27,0:14:39.02,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,Twenty kilometers southeast!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.02,0:14:41.56,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,The boss's daughter Trish \N is somewhere in that area!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.61,0:14:46.74,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,I did it! \N I don't need shit from you anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.45,0:14:57.87,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,My Aerosmith has the ability to \Ntrack carbon dioxide...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.33,0:15:03.59,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,...but carbon dioxide doesn't just \N come from living creatures...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.59,0:15:06.59,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,It also comes from burning things...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:09.93,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,I remembered something...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.43,0:15:13.51,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,When I was tracking you with Aerosmith...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.51,0:15:15.97,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,...I also shot at a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.97,0:15:20.89,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,I think I hit the gas tank...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.89,0:15:25.32,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,...but I can't really tell\N where the holes are from here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.32,0:15:26.44,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.98,0:15:36.08,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,I figured since the bullet holes are still technically burning, \N Aerosmith could find them using the carbon dioxide.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.45,0:15:38.25,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,So I shot at them...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.25,0:15:41.75,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,I wasn't trying to shoot the spider earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.75,0:15:48.42,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,I was starting to freak out since it took a while \N to make a big enough fire with my tiny-ass bullets!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.42,0:15:49.84,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:03.35,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.35,0:16:09.07,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1065)}All the shit I bought is toast! {Original: "All the shopping bags got burned up!"}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.07,0:16:14.87,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,But man, it feels great to be big enough \N that a little spider bite won't hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.87,0:16:16.53,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,How dare you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.91,0:16:21.50,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,I'm gonna fucking kill all your friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:24.46,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,Hideout...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.96,0:16:27.34,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,Vineyard...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.34,0:16:31.67,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,Just fucking wait, Narancia!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.63,0:16:35.64,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,Little Feat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:40.10,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.56,0:16:45.52,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,He stopped the fire by \N spraying blood out of his wrists?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.52,0:16:47.56,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Dammit! This sucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.56,0:16:49.82,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,This is gonna get ugly if he gets away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.82,0:16:52.03,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,I have to find him using Aerosmith's ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.40,0:16:55.32,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Sh-Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.32,0:16:57.12,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Th-The radar...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.12,0:16:58.95,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,These flames... {Again, this sounds like a mixing error :| }
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.49,0:17:03.58,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,{\an8}Y-You motherfucker! Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.49,0:17:02.70,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,Is this good luck or bad luck?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.70,0:17:07.08,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,Narancia, now that you've set the car on fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.33,0:17:13.34,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,...you can't track me because of \N all the carbon dioxide coming from the flames!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.34,0:17:17.01,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,If there's gotta be a winner and a loser, \N then I'm the winner!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.80,0:17:15.18,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,{\an8}You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.01,0:17:19.35,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,I know where the boss's daughter is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.35,0:17:22.77,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,Now I just need to get out of here and tell the team! {No -J}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.02,0:17:25.73,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,We'll kill you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.73,0:17:29.40,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,Assassination is what we do!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.40,0:17:30.19,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Assassination?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.19,0:17:32.86,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,I'll have my revenge soon enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.86,0:17:34.78,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,You'll never find me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.78,0:17:37.86,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.62,0:17:47.17,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,If I can't track your breathing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.17,0:17:50.79,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,If the flames are too big...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.79,0:17:54.01,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,...then I'll just make them bigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.43,0:18:07.64,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,If I set the whole fucking street on fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.64,0:18:10.73,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,...you'll burn up and die since you're so tiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.40,0:18:14.74,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,You're not getting away, Formaggio!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.74,0:18:19.70,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,Are you insane, motherfucker?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.62,0:18:23.41,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,You seriously set the whole street on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.41,0:18:26.37,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,Are you out of your mind? {The "Fuck you" might be character-appropriate but this is all he literally says, and really, having an insult thrown in BETWEEN "Are you out of your mind" and "Huh" seemed weird to me. -Starfish the careful analyzer of profanity}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.66,0:18:28.00,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.58,0:18:32.59,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Well, you just saved me the trouble \N of setting the whole city on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.59,0:18:35.51,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,The reason I asked if \N you were out of your mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.51,0:18:41.55,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,...is because you're practically begging me \N to kill you as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.14,0:18:46.60,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,Thanks to the flames, \N I'm up close and personal with you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.60,0:18:47.81,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,Did you forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.10,0:18:52.69,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,At this distance, my Stand is faster than yours! {MY PAIN IS GREATER THAN YOURS!!!!!!!!!!!}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.69,0:18:53.57,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.57,0:18:56.07,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,Bring it, Narancia...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.33,0:19:10.08,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,Little Feat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:19.30,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,Guess you win... {"shou ga nee na..."}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.80,0:19:25.14,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,But your little shopping trip \N wasn't as easy as you thought it'd be, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.43,0:19:27.85,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,Eh, Narancia?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.85,0:19:33.86,Main,Formaggio,0,0,0,,Shit's about to get {\i1}real{\i0} difficult \N for you motherfuckers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.11,0:19:42.11,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,"Go shopping," they told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.03,0:19:48.08,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Mission... failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.08,0:19:50.00,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,My money and all the stuff I bought...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:53.00,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,...went up in flames...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:57.21,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,Narancia, repeat that to me one more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.21,0:19:59.05,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,I told you, the shopping{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.05,0:20:00.38,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,Not that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.38,0:20:03.26,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,You just said the enemy \N found out where we're hiding!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.26,0:20:04.64,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,But I took care of him right af{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.64,0:20:06.81,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,That's not the issue here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.81,0:20:09.93,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Buccellati, we need to ditch this place, pronto.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.93,0:20:12.02,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,After I warned you so many times...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.02,0:20:13.52,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,You fool! {there's that word again. Dunce, maybe? -JMFW}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.52,0:20:18.28,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,It seems to me that Narancia did a great job \N of foiling the enemy's plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.98,0:20:22.74,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,He did what was necessary, \N given the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.74,0:20:27.45,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,And now that the Hitman Team \N knows our location, any wise boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.45,0:20:30.62,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,...would surely instruct us \N how to make our escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.87,0:20:36.71,Main,Giorno,0,0,0,,It would be unwise to leave \N until we receive word from the boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.71,0:20:38.88,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,Well, aren't you clever?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.88,0:20:40.80,Main,Fugo,0,0,0,,Are you our advisor now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.21,0:20:45.72,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,And just how do you know the boss \N is gonna make contact with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.72,0:20:47.64,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,We don't give a fuck \N about your little hunches!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.64,0:20:48.56,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Buccellati!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.56,0:20:51.06,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,I think we just got \N a message from the boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.77,0:21:00.94,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,The boss always sends his orders \N to the capos this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.94,0:21:03.90,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,This is the first time \N Buccellati's received one!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.78,0:21:06.11,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Let's see what it says.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.16,0:21:14.92,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,"Head to the Archaeological Park of Pompeii{http://pompeiisites.org/en/archaeological-park-of-pompeii/about-us/}. \NI've hidden a key near the dog mosaic{https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/320639391674400770/524381085421928452/84508818_pompeiidogepa.png}."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.92,0:21:15.92,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Look into this immediately! {"Get on this, now!" might be a bit terse for the Bucc, but we're not sure of any other ways we could shorten it. Reason: CPS -JMFW/Toa}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.25,0:21:27.43,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,"This key is for a vehicle which will \N safely deliver my daughter to me."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.43,0:21:30.39,Main,Abbacchio,0,0,0,,Vehicle? \N What does he mean by a safe vehicle?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.39,0:21:32.22,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,A helicopter!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.22,0:21:34.73,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,It's gotta be a helicopter key!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.73,0:21:37.69,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,We can go wherever we want in a helicopter \N without anyone following us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.10,0:21:41.27,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,It's a bit less than fifteen kilometers \N from here to Pompeii.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.27,0:21:45.28,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,An hour should be plenty of time \N to go there and retrieve the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.28,0:21:47.99,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Fugo! Abbacchio! Giorno!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.99,0:21:50.78,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,You three head to Pompeii \N and retrieve that key!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.28,0:21:55.54,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Mista, Narancia, and I will stay here \N and protect Trish from the Hitman Team.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.04,0:21:59.75,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Retrieve the key, \N then contact me once it's safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.75,0:22:03.67,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Then we'll take Trish \N and head over to the vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.71,0:22:05.80,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you.
